com.ojcoleman.europa.core

Class Log

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ojcoleman.europa.core.Log

  • public class Log
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to specify and record log items. Used in methods like Transcriber.transcribe(Genotype, Function) and Evaluator.evaluate(Individual, Log) so that they may record implementation-specific details of the process they perform.
    Author:
    O. J. Coleman
